AVG Ultimate Multi-Device

The best in online protection, performance, and privacy.

AVG Ultimate is a complete bundle of AVG’s antivirus, tuneup, anti-track and VPN products. With Ultimate, you can either enhance one device, or you can secure and optimize up to 10 with our multi-device package — perfect for sharing online privacy, digital security, and boosted performance with your friends or family.

Enjoy our advanced real-time security, which protects against ransomware, spyware, and other malware, as well as hackers.
Free up disk space, find and remove hidden duplicate files, and delete poor-quality photos to improve the speed and performance of your device.
Use our fast and simple VPN and automatic anti-track to hide your online activities from hackers, spies, your ISP, advertisers, and even the government.

AVG Internet Security for Windows

Our absolute best antivirus combines artificial intelligence with a huge malware-detecting network to keep your PC free of malware, hackers, and spies.

AVG Internet Security for Mac

Not even Macs are safe from malware. AVG Internet Security protects your Mac so viruses, spyware, ransomware, and hackers can’t cause any trouble.

AVG AntiVirus for Android AVG Mobile Security for iPhone & iPad

Block malware and unsafe apps, and secure your vulnerable personal data with our most complete protection for Android and iOS devices.

AVG Secure VPN for Windows, Mac, Android, and iOS

Ensure your browsing, banking, and everything you do online stay hidden and protected, whether you’re at home or using public Wi-Fi.

AVG TuneUp for Windows

Clean junk files to free up storage space, put unused apps to sleep, boost startup speeds, and even set automatic cleanings.

AVG TuneUp for Mac

Clean and optimize your Mac. Get rid of junk files, duplicates, bad-quality photos, and enjoy all the extra drive space you forgot you had.

AVG Cleaner for Android

Enjoy a longer lasting battery, clear out duplicate and unwanted photos, and genuinely make your phone the best it can be with one easy tap.

Stop advertisers from following your online trail and harassing you with targeted ads.
